snippet.title: HOW TO Install THUG Pro
snippet.description:
The Tony Hawk's Games bring a lot of nostalgia to me as I am sure they do many other people. This video shows how to install the THUG Pro mod to Tony Hawks Underground 2.


▼THUG PRO Installer▼
http://thugpro.com/

▼Instagram▼
https://www.instagram.com/super_lentendo/

If this video was helpful, please like, share and comment. If you would like to see further content from me, please subscribe :)
